{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"gzy1xz97zvnttb8urqpfhh3","title":"Flavor Flash Journal","desc":"","updated":1703388640780,"created":1700872379646,"custom":{},"fname":"programming.side projects.flavor flash journal","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"38e303a7beaf40b221d002d760a6e1e7","links":[],"anchors":{"food-app":{"type":"header","text":"Food App","value":"food-app","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["eprh315gok7nqhqxs1dyos3","itzjg71gb2k0xaj8p8a0a9b","viioqk5u9v3rsmcfvb5zv3l","pe6vepkpwtgibepjb75nfmg","idmoihik9jm09tb79mbpk1q","rj6d1s24ldccufdqi31lhmn","dy8x4ijvphppvx2ruts6lxv","xjoeuc8wuqj1r0fwoesk2k1","v23jjeviz0i0ms8c7nkbkfa","9mr2s7gpmdzbi4penck2gg0","gl20na8txb9ctwgns65tbeb","b1h5ug1zl5ba1h28rcunyia","efb7lxnmysqpsnu2ldh7b0r","snyjwumcbhskqfobufygzto","ftar26pjpxmmjemznet1npi","0zd97egyho7luqqur6n5wnu"],"parent":"yr68nymrc2wmccpkch7bxf2","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"flavor-flash-journal\">Flavor Flash Journal<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#flavor-flash-journal\"></a></h1>\n<p>Flavor Flash 開發筆記</p>\n<h2 id=\"food-app\">Food App<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#food-app\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>TA:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>喜歡被動探索美食的人</li>\n<li>有選擇障礙 / 不想花時間想要吃什麼的人</li>\n<li>喜歡紀錄食物口感的人</li>\n<li>google評論有時候可以被刷出來、不如朋友圈一起建立可信的美食地圖</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Feature:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>隨機選食物 -> 找附近的餐廳</li>\n<li>左滑右滑收藏餐廳 (餐廳抽卡,UI要炫砲)</li>\n<li>美食日記\n<ol>\n<li>飢餓狀態</li>\n<li>上傳圖片，\n<ol>\n<li>後鏡頭拍食物分析食物的標籤(分析不準也可帶入自定義標籤)</li>\n<li>前鏡頭拍人像分析人臉（喜怒哀樂）作為評價</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>寫下心得</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>可以查看自己曾到訪的餐廳，針對吃的次數給不同顏色圖釘、註解</li>\n<li>好友的頁面可以查看他的美食日記、以及他的美食地圖(曾到訪的餐廳)</li>\n<li>聊天系統\n<ol>\n<li>1對1</li>\n<li>群組</li>\n<li>傳jpg、png、gif</li>\n<li>分享餐廳資訊</li>\n<li>(optional)影片</li>\n<li>(optional)投票要吃的餐廳</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>成就勳章：（月結、週結、小任務）\n<ol>\n<li>很常吃飯 => 飯桶</li>\n<li>常常不同的餐廳 => 發現新大陸</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>週飲食習慣、月飲食習慣分析(3D呈現)</li>\n<li>APP顏色要可切換</li>\n<li>日曆簽到系統，當天有發美食日記的話就算簽到成功</li>\n<li>動態島、鎖屏提示(Activity Kit)</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>預計需要學的東西:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>MapKit\n<ol>\n<li>Marker &#x26; Annotation</li>\n<li>selection</li>\n<li>contentBuilder</li>\n<li>mapStyle</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>SpriteKit</li>\n<li>AVFoundation</li>\n<li>CoreML\n<ol>\n<li>Vision</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>Firebase APIs</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>reference:\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/PCChuang/Subminder\">https://github.com/PCChuang/Subminder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/TaiHsin/Travel\">https://github.com/TaiHsin/Travel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pisck888/Hahabbit\">https://github.com/pisck888/Hahabbit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/thisisalliet/FocusFoodie\">https://github.com/thisisalliet/FocusFoodie</a></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/programming_notes/assets/images/ifoodie-webconfig.png\"></p>\n<p>我這次個人專案開發的是一款探索及紀錄美食的app，那會想要開發這款app的原因是因為我每天都會遇到午餐晚餐要吃什麼的問題，再加上女朋友有紀錄以及分享美食的習慣，於是我就決定以這兩個需求去開發這款美食App。</p>\n<p>首先，首頁放的是我自己最常使用的功能，那我的使用情境就是在每天中午不知道要吃什麼時候就可以打開來點一下，並且透過調整地圖參數去調整你想看到的餐廳搜尋結果。</p>\n<p>那進到地圖搜尋的頁面時，使用者可以透過點擊圖釘以及下方的餐廳卡片去移動到該餐廳的位置，點擊下方卡片也可以看到餐廳的基本資料。</p>\n<p>如果我在瀏覽餐廳的時候看到了幾間還不錯的餐廳，我也可以餐廳資訊這邊先加到我的待吃清單，等到下一餐又不知道要吃什麼的時候，也可以從待吃的清單去做選擇。</p>\n<p>那如果在地圖上有看到這餐想吃的餐廳時，你就可以點擊該餐廳的圖釘然後點旁邊的地圖icon去開啟apple map的導航。</p>\n<p>那回到首頁點擊收藏的ICON就可以看到你待吃名單中的餐廳有哪些，如果吃了就可以把該餐廳移除待吃名單。</p>\n<p>那這是探索附近餐廳的功能，接下來要帶過的是記錄美食的功能，使用者可以點擊這個相機的icon開啟前後鏡頭，開啟後使用者可以對鏡頭的顯示做一些調整，查看有沒有死角。</p>\n<p>拍好之後也可以再次確認照片沒有問題，做一些簡單的編輯，那如果沒有問題就可以進一步寫下心得。</p>\n<p>發文美食評論之後就可在美食足跡的社群中，看到自己跟朋友的發文，你可以對貼文留言&#x26;按讚。那如果有一些私底下想詢問的美食問題，也可以去聊天室建立群組聊天。</p>\n<p>那除了在這個社群頁面可以看到其他朋友的發文，使用者也可以在個人頁面的foodprint中在地圖上查看他過往吃過的餐廳，也可以跟朋友做足跡的疊加。</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/eprh315gok7nqhqxs1dyos3\">Animation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/idmoihik9jm09tb79mbpk1q\">Architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/rj6d1s24ldccufdqi31lhmn\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/dy8x4ijvphppvx2ruts6lxv\">Concurrency</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/xjoeuc8wuqj1r0fwoesk2k1\">Core Data</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/v23jjeviz0i0ms8c7nkbkfa\">Data Structure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/9mr2s7gpmdzbi4penck2gg0\">Dependency Injection</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/itzjg71gb2k0xaj8p8a0a9b\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/gl20na8txb9ctwgns65tbeb\">Firebase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/efb7lxnmysqpsnu2ldh7b0r\">Mapkit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/snyjwumcbhskqfobufygzto\">Style Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/ftar26pjpxmmjemznet1npi\">Test</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/viioqk5u9v3rsmcfvb5zv3l\">Tips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/pe6vepkpwtgibepjb75nfmg\">View</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/0zd97egyho7luqqur6n5wnu\">Xcode Issues</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/programming_notes/notes/b1h5ug1zl5ba1h28rcunyia\">iOS Version Check</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"","updated":1605266684036,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"b49e7e13a0c91addc8ab9ef97080cf1e","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":["p1jj2aztluo4pb12qn8gunp","avquk6puzxi790rxzodnfmh","rn0e0y5coqo8iyqfxd7ocsk","c1bs7wsjfbhb0zipaywqv1"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nThis is the root for your Dendron vault.\n\nIf you decide to publish your entire vault, it will be your landing page. You are free to customize any part of this page except the frontmatter at the top, between the `---`.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMod